30003911@@@@@@Background@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:139; ntucle-sid:1101@LMC@2019-06-14
30003912@@@@@@There has been a significant increase in food wastage in Singapore over the past decade.@@@@1@15@ntucle-docid:139; ntucle-sid:1102@LMC@2019-06-14
