30004066@@@@@@The display then generates a QR code with instructions on prize redemption.@@@@1@12@ntucle-docid:143; ntucle-sid:948@LMC@2019-06-14
30004067@@@@@@The key here is to make the incentive something attractive, which all people could use, such as supermarket vouchers.@@@@1@19@ntucle-docid:143; ntucle-sid:949@LMC@2019-06-14
