30004130@@@@@@Ez-Link Mobile App (E-zapp)@@@@1@4@ntucle-docid:145; ntucle-sid:907@LMC@2019-06-14
30004131@@@@@@Background@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:145; ntucle-sid:908@LMC@2019-06-14
30004132@@@@@@Transportation plays a very important part in everyone’s life.@@@@1@9@ntucle-docid:145; ntucle-sid:909@LMC@2019-06-14
30004133@@@@@@According to the national statistics, average utilization of public transport is about 6,356,000 passenger trip per day [1].@@@@1@18@ntucle-docid:145; ntucle-sid:910@LMC@2019-06-14
30004134@@@@@@Majority of the commuters use EZ-link cards to pay for their fares.@@@@1@12@ntucle-docid:145; ntucle-sid:911@LMC@2019-06-14
30004135@@@@@@EZ-link cards are contactless smartcards where users will load some value into the card before using it for payments [2].@@@@1@20@ntucle-docid:145; ntucle-sid:912@LMC@2019-06-14
30004136@@@@@@Low card value has always been a problem for commuters using EZ-link card.@@@@1@13@ntucle-docid:145; ntucle-sid:913@LMC@2019-06-14
30004137@@@@@@Commuters usually tap in and out of the gantry and card reader, without taking a closer look at their card value.@@@@1@21@ntucle-docid:145; ntucle-sid:914@LMC@2019-06-14
30004138@@@@@@Problem@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:145; ntucle-sid:915@LMC@2019-06-14
30004139@@@@@@While card readers do signal to the commuters when their card values are running low, people tend to overlook this trivial matter.@@@@1@22@ntucle-docid:145; ntucle-sid:916@LMC@2019-06-14
30004140@@@@@@Whenever there is low card value, commuters will have to queue up at top-up stations to top-up their cards.@@@@1@19@ntucle-docid:145; ntucle-sid:917@LMC@2019-06-14
30004141@@@@@@Majority of the commuters will definitely find this troublesome and time consuming.@@@@1@12@ntucle-docid:145; ntucle-sid:918@LMC@2019-06-14
30004142@@@@@@Furthermore, when EZ-link cards have insufficient values, commuters are not allowed to enter the MRT gantry or board the bus, causing inconvenience to them.@@@@1@24@ntucle-docid:145; ntucle-sid:919@LMC@2019-06-14
30004143@@@@@@Current online reload service requires commuters to purchase an external card reader and install it into their computers [3].@@@@1@19@ntucle-docid:145; ntucle-sid:920@LMC@2019-06-14
30004144@@@@@@Commuters are deterred from using this service as they have to spend extra cash and trouble to get an EZ-link card reader and installing it in order to enjoy this convenience.@@@@1@31@ntucle-docid:145; ntucle-sid:921@LMC@2019-06-14
30004145@@@@@@Solution@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:145; ntucle-sid:922@LMC@2019-06-14
30004146@@@@@@A secured mobile application can be developed to allow commuters to check their card value, top-up their card on the go and even report a lost or stolen card.@@@@1@29@ntucle-docid:145; ntucle-sid:923@LMC@2019-06-14
30004147@@@@@@Commuters will first set-up an account and register their card using the unique C.A.N number found at the back of EZ-link card.@@@@1@22@ntucle-docid:145; ntucle-sid:924@LMC@2019-06-14
30004148@@@@@@Data of the card such as the balanced value will be stored in the account and linked to the mobile application.@@@@1@21@ntucle-docid:145; ntucle-sid:925@LMC@2019-06-14
30004149@@@@@@When commuters open the mobile application, they will enter a four digits passcode before proceeding to the home page.@@@@1@19@ntucle-docid:145; ntucle-sid:926@LMC@2019-06-14
30004150@@@@@@To top-up the card, commuters will enter the value to top-up and the bill will be charged to their credit or debit card.@@@@1@23@ntucle-docid:145; ntucle-sid:927@LMC@2019-06-14
30004151@@@@@@The new balance will be reflected immediately.@@@@1@7@ntucle-docid:145; ntucle-sid:928@LMC@2019-06-14
30004152@@@@@@When commuters misplaced their card, they can suspend it and the stored value will be transferred to their new card.@@@@1@20@ntucle-docid:145; ntucle-sid:929@LMC@2019-06-14
30004153@@@@@@Benefits@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:145; ntucle-sid:930@LMC@2019-06-14
30004154@@@@@@This allows commuters to check the stored value and top-up their EZ-link card during their free time.@@@@1@17@ntucle-docid:145; ntucle-sid:931@LMC@2019-06-14
30004155@@@@@@This reduces the hassle of queuing at the top-up kiosk, saving commuters’ time and avoid a delay of journey.@@@@1@19@ntucle-docid:145; ntucle-sid:932@LMC@2019-06-14
30004156@@@@@@This also results in a shorter queues for commuters who do not have access to this application.@@@@1@17@ntucle-docid:145; ntucle-sid:933@LMC@2019-06-14
30004157@@@@@@Cost@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:145; ntucle-sid:934@LMC@2019-06-14
