30004159@@@@@@Implementation@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:145; ntucle-sid:936@LMC@2019-06-14
30004160@@@@@@The process of developing an application will be:@@@@1@8@ntucle-docid:145; ntucle-sid:937@LMC@2019-06-14
30004161@@@@@@1@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:145; ntucle-sid:938@LMC@2019-06-14
