30004285@@@@@@Background:@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:151; ntucle-sid:1005@LMC@2019-06-14
30004286@@@@@@When travelling to an unfamiliar place, many commuters tend to get lost.@@@@1@12@ntucle-docid:151; ntucle-sid:1006@LMC@2019-06-14
30004287@@@@@@In Singapore, there are bus applications that assist commuters to get to a destination.@@@@1@14@ntucle-docid:151; ntucle-sid:1007@LMC@2019-06-14
30004288@@@@@@However, these applications do not inform the users beforehand which bus stop they should alight at.@@@@1@16@ntucle-docid:151; ntucle-sid:1008@LMC@2019-06-14
30004289@@@@@@Hence, increasing the chances of the user dropping at the wrong stop and losing their way.@@@@1@16@ntucle-docid:151; ntucle-sid:1009@LMC@2019-06-14
30004290@@@@@@Problem:@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:151; ntucle-sid:1010@LMC@2019-06-14
30004291@@@@@@Existing bus applications (e.g.@@@@1@4@ntucle-docid:151; ntucle-sid:1011@LMC@2019-06-14
30004292@@@@@@Google Maps) are good at giving directions by suggesting different routes to direct us from one point to another by stating the name of the bus stop to alight at.@@@@1@30@ntucle-docid:151; ntucle-sid:1012@LMC@2019-06-14
30004293@@@@@@However, commuters may not recognize the surroundings of the place and could be unsure even after knowing the name of the bus stop.@@@@1@23@ntucle-docid:151; ntucle-sid:1013@LMC@2019-06-14
30004294@@@@@@This would cause the commuter to alight earlier or later.@@@@1@10@ntucle-docid:151; ntucle-sid:1014@LMC@2019-06-14
30004295@@@@@@Solution:@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:151; ntucle-sid:1015@LMC@2019-06-14
30004296@@@@@@To curb this problem, the Bus Alarm application will be integrated to the existing bus applications.@@@@1@16@ntucle-docid:151; ntucle-sid:1016@LMC@2019-06-14
30004297@@@@@@The Bus Alarm uses the user’s phone location to identify which bus stop the user is at and the user will be alerted one stop before their chosen bus stop location.@@@@1@31@ntucle-docid:151; ntucle-sid:1017@LMC@2019-06-14
30004298@@@@@@Besides that, it is able to pick up on the subsequent bus stop name and the number of bus stops before the user’s stop.@@@@1@24@ntucle-docid:151; ntucle-sid:1018@LMC@2019-06-14
30004299@@@@@@Added features like the estimated time between each bus stop depending on the traffic and a wake up alarm can be used to alert the user to alight the bus if he falls asleep.@@@@1@34@ntucle-docid:151; ntucle-sid:1019@LMC@2019-06-14
