30004327@@@@@@Title of Proposal: Improvement of Singapore Public Transport Apps@@@@1@9@ntucle-docid:152; ntucle-sid:1045@LMC@2019-06-14
30004328@@@@@@Improvement of Singapore Public Transport Apps@@@@1@6@ntucle-docid:152; ntucle-sid:1050@LMC@2019-06-14
30004329@@@@@@Background@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:152; ntucle-sid:1051@LMC@2019-06-14
30004330@@@@@@Punctuality plays an important role in the society.@@@@1@8@ntucle-docid:152; ntucle-sid:1052@LMC@2019-06-14
30004331@@@@@@(Mokhtar, 2011) stated that according to the Singapore satisfactory statistic report conducted in 2011, 35% of the respondents were not satisfied about the arrival times of the public transport.@@@@1@29@ntucle-docid:152; ntucle-sid:1053@LMC@2019-06-14
30004332@@@@@@(Fang, 2014) stated that 2014 holds the highest record of train delays of twelve incidents in the first nine months as compared to 2011, which had eleven incidents.@@@@1@28@ntucle-docid:152; ntucle-sid:1054@LMC@2019-06-14
30004333@@@@@@Hence, the punctuality of the affected commuters reaching their designated places is a concern.@@@@1@14@ntucle-docid:152; ntucle-sid:1055@LMC@2019-06-14
30004334@@@@@@Problem@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:152; ntucle-sid:1056@LMC@2019-06-14
30004335@@@@@@To deter this problem, there are many local public transport smartphone apps available with the warning notification service to alert users of any disruptions of affected train lines during that period, the arrival time of buses at any bus stops and the journey duration for any transport route.@@@@1@48@ntucle-docid:152; ntucle-sid:1057@LMC@2019-06-14
30004336@@@@@@Since commuters cannot do anything to improve the transport system, these apps can be further improved to help plan out the user’s punctuality more effectively.@@@@1@25@ntucle-docid:152; ntucle-sid:1058@LMC@2019-06-14
30004337@@@@@@Solution@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:152; ntucle-sid:1059@LMC@2019-06-14
30004338@@@@@@The main goal of this proposal is to enhance the public transport app to benefit users effectively for punctuality.@@@@1@19@ntucle-docid:152; ntucle-sid:1060@LMC@2019-06-14
30004339@@@@@@Firstly, a “journey planner” will not only provide the journey time, but also plan out the time so as to let users reach their destination on time.@@@@1@27@ntucle-docid:152; ntucle-sid:1061@LMC@2019-06-14
30004340@@@@@@The users need to input their destination, starting point, the meeting time and their choice of transport route.@@@@1@18@ntucle-docid:152; ntucle-sid:1062@LMC@2019-06-14
30004341@@@@@@Secondly, an alert can be issued to notify the users of nearby buses approaching within range.@@@@1@16@ntucle-docid:152; ntucle-sid:1063@LMC@2019-06-14
