30004369@@@@@@[2]Finally, use your phone to touch the name of the restaurant on the poster, the NFC chip under it will request your phone to send this message with your GPS address to the restaurant preset number.@@@@1@36@ntucle-docid:153; ntucle-sid:1067@LMC@2019-06-14
