30004513@@@@@@Go Safe, Go Card-less@@@@1@4@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1436@LMC@2019-06-14
30004514@@@@@@Assignment 1: Technical Proposal@@@@1@4@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1439@LMC@2019-06-14
30004515@@@@@@Go safe, go card-less@@@@1@4@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1443@LMC@2019-06-14
30004516@@@@@@Background@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1444@LMC@2019-06-14
30004517@@@@@@Theft is an inevitable crime but it can be avoided by taking precautions.@@@@1@13@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1445@LMC@2019-06-14
30004518@@@@@@Cashcard theft is one of the easiest thefts which occur due to the driver’s carelessness and negligence of leaving their cashcards inserted in their vehicles’ IU (inspection unit).@@@@1@28@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1446@LMC@2019-06-14
30004519@@@@@@Just last year, a couple have been arrested over a series of cashcard theft from more than 20 vehicles, amounting to about $190.@@@@1@23@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1447@LMC@2019-06-14
30004520@@@@@@[1] In a more recent case, in January 2015, a 26 year old man was arrested for stealing a cashcard from a lorry.@@@@1@23@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1448@LMC@2019-06-14
30004521@@@@@@[2] These repeating cases of cashcard theft from vehicles is becoming more of a concern in our society.@@@@1@18@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1449@LMC@2019-06-14
30004522@@@@@@Problem@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1450@LMC@2019-06-14
30004523@@@@@@It is human nature to forget.@@@@1@6@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1451@LMC@2019-06-14
30004524@@@@@@People always rush and do not always check if they have left any valuables in their vehicles after parking.@@@@1@19@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1452@LMC@2019-06-14
30004525@@@@@@Usually, a cashcard is inserted in the IU, so it is easy to not notice whether their cashcards have been removed.@@@@1@21@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1453@LMC@2019-06-14
30004526@@@@@@Every year, there would be cases of cashcard theft.@@@@1@9@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1454@LMC@2019-06-14
30004527@@@@@@Victims would find their vehicles’ window smashed.@@@@1@7@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1455@LMC@2019-06-14
30004528@@@@@@Although not many motorists would deposit a lot of money in their cashcards, such acts cause a lot of trouble for the affected owners, who would have to fork out a large sum for repairs, and have to experience the inconvenience of not having the car to drive.@@@@1@48@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1456@LMC@2019-06-14
30004529@@@@@@Solution@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1457@LMC@2019-06-14
30004530@@@@@@The main goal of this proposal is to introduce card-less IUs.@@@@1@11@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1458@LMC@2019-06-14
30004531@@@@@@Instead of having to slot in a cashcard in the IU, a value-storing microchip is embedded inside it to allow card-less transaction on the road.@@@@1@25@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1459@LMC@2019-06-14
30004532@@@@@@The idea is to eliminate the use of cards for fee deduction of car park gantries and ERPs.@@@@1@18@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1460@LMC@2019-06-14
30004533@@@@@@There will be the same procedure of deducting value when passing a gantry, but the value will be deducted from the microchip inside the IU.@@@@1@25@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1461@LMC@2019-06-14
30004534@@@@@@Motorists can top up their IUs using the serial number through iBanking or ATMs.@@@@1@14@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1462@LMC@2019-06-14
30004535@@@@@@When insufficient value is detected, the IU will beep to notify the user to add value for next usage.@@@@1@19@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1463@LMC@2019-06-14
30004536@@@@@@Benefits@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1464@LMC@2019-06-14
30004537@@@@@@By going card-less, there will not be any temptation to steal from vehicles.@@@@1@13@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1465@LMC@2019-06-14
30004538@@@@@@Vehicle owners need not worry if they have removed their cashcards.@@@@1@11@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1466@LMC@2019-06-14
30004539@@@@@@Thus, the crime rate for cashcard theft will be low as it is not possible to steal an IU from a vehicle.@@@@1@22@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1467@LMC@2019-06-14
30004540@@@@@@Implementation@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1468@LMC@2019-06-14
30004541@@@@@@1@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1469@LMC@2019-06-14
30004542@@@@@@Collaborate with the manufacturer of vehicle inspection units to install a value storing and deducting chip inside the IU (similar to EZ-Link).@@@@1@22@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1470@LMC@2019-06-14
30004543@@@@@@2@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1471@LMC@2019-06-14
30004544@@@@@@Advertise to LTA for approval@@@@1@5@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1472@LMC@2019-06-14
