30004550@@@@@@Conclusion@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1478@LMC@2019-06-14
30004551@@@@@@The risk of daily thefts happening is unavoidable.@@@@1@8@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1479@LMC@2019-06-14
30004552@@@@@@This is why we should take measures to limit the chances of theft from vehicles.@@@@1@15@ntucle-docid:157; ntucle-sid:1480@LMC@2019-06-14
